00:26:10,304 --> 00:26:12,421
Tidak.

245
00:26:14,842 --> 00:26:17,259
Jadi mengapa kita berdua tak bisa tidur?

246
00:26:25,686 --> 00:26:27,686
Aku akan berjalan-jalan.

247
00:26:42,753 --> 00:26:44,870
<i>Kau Rick.</i>

248
00:26:50,127 --> 00:26:51,543
Benar.

249
00:26:52,797 --> 00:26:54,797
Istriku memotong rambutmu.

250
00:26:56,934 --> 00:26:58,850
Benar.

251
00:27:02,940 --> 00:27:05,357
Selamat Datang di Alexandria.

