Lihatlah ini.

322
00:36:01,955 --> 00:36:04,506
Darahnya masih basah.
Pasti tak jauh.

323
00:36:07,094 --> 00:36:11,963
Hei, dia sudah menghilang. /
Dia menghabisi salah satu kawan kami.

324
00:36:11,965 --> 00:36:13,515
Kami takkan biarkan mereka pergi.

325
00:36:17,804 --> 00:36:23,108
Kemarilah.

326
00:36:23,110 --> 00:36:25,193
Jangan tembak. /
Kalian mundur.

327
00:36:25,195 --> 00:36:30,064
Kemarilah.
Kemarilah.

328
00:36:32,285 --> 00:36:33,985
<i>Tangkap dia.</i>

329
00:36:42,996 --> 00:36:44,829
<i>Tidak, Pegang dia.</i>

330
00:36:51,588 --> 00:36:54,005
Apa-apaan? /
Ya, apa-apaan kau?

331
00:36:54,007 --> 00:36:56,891
Kau hampir saja membuatnya terbunuh. /
Sudah kubilang mundur.

